{
  "texts": [
    "Using the historical context that an LLM could process, the agent could flag usage that deviates from historical use.",
    "The role of the Patra repository then is to notify the agent each time there is a new deployment of a model card.More broadly this interaction between data store and AI agent is cast as an interaction method such as the ReAct (Reson + Act) method [7].",
    "In this method, an agent presents the state of the world to an LLM, solicits LLM response, then asks the LLM what it wants to do next.",
    "An agent begins by writing a thought about the given task.",
    "The agent then performs an action based on that thought, and the output is observed."
  ]
}